                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.93/73.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul <persName type="from">Letcher</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Chihuahua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-04-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 30, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Newspaper report that some modification of ordinary restriction against entrance
                    of Japanese and Chinese is now in force. Information is requested, principally
                    in interest of Chinese.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Letcher</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
